							GitHub
						</a>
						<a class="secondary" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/alikarakoc/" target="_blank">
							<svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" aria-hidden="true"><path fill="currentColor" d="M1.146 1.146C1.523.77 2.06.5 2.75.5s1.227.27 1.604.646c.377.377.646.914.646 1.604 0 .69-.27 1.227-.646 1.604-.377.377-.914.646-1.604.646s-1.227-.27-1.604-.646C.77 3.977.5 3.44.5 2.75c0-.69.27-1.227.646-1.604zM.5 5.5h4.5v10H.5v-10zm6 0h4.3v1.367h.062c.598-1.133 2.062-2.33 4.238-2.33 4.533 0 5.362 2.983 5.362 6.858V15.5h-4.5v-4.7c0-1.122-.02-2.566-1.563-2.566-1.566 0-1.805 1.223-1.805 2.484V15.5H6.5v-10z"/></svg>
							LinkedIn
						</a>
